# Virtual Data Room (VDR) Assistant — MVP Handoff Document

## Overview

The project is a retrieval-first Virtual Data Room assistant designed for internal M&A / diligence workflows.

The assistant allows users to ask questions against uploaded VDR documents and receive:
- grounded answers only
- supporting excerpts
- source document references
- folder hierarchy metadata
- page / slide / sheet references
- direct document access links where possible

The assistant is explicitly NOT intended to:
- provide speculative reasoning
- use general model knowledge
- act as an autonomous diligence advisor
- infer conclusions not explicitly supported by uploaded documents

Core philosophy:
- trustworthiness over creativity
- evidence retrieval over synthesis
- completeness and traceability over conversational fluency

---

